  <compounddef id="CLS" kind="page">
    <compoundname>CLS</compoundname>
    <title>CLS Keyword</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">CLS</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Clears <bold>everything on screen</bold> - both the text display and any graphics - and moves the cursor to the <bold>top-left</bold> <computeroutput>(0,0)</computeroutput>.</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>The current foreground and background <bold>colours are not reset</bold>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Subsequent text and graphics draw onto a blank screen using the active colours.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><heading level="5">Example</heading>
</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;Hello!&quot;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">CIRCLE<sp/>200,<sp/>150,<sp/>50,<sp/>TRUE</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">SLEEP<sp/>1</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">CLS</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">PRINT<sp/>&quot;Screen<sp/>cleared.&quot;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><heading level="5">Notes</heading>
</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><computeroutput>CLS</computeroutput> removes previously drawn graphics (e.g. from <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/LINE"><computeroutput>LINE</computeroutput></ulink>, <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/RECTANGLE"><computeroutput>RECTANGLE</computeroutput></ulink>, <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/CIRCLE"><computeroutput>CIRCLE</computeroutput></ulink>, etc.) as well as text.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Colours set with <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/COLOUR"><computeroutput>COLOUR</computeroutput></ulink> or <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/BACKGROUND"><computeroutput>BACKGROUND</computeroutput></ulink> <bold>remain in effect</bold> after a clear.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/COLOUR"><computeroutput>COLOUR</computeroutput></ulink>, <ulink url="https://github.com/brainboxdotcc/retro-rocket/wiki/BACKGROUND"><computeroutput>BACKGROUND</computeroutput></ulink> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
